Agregar discos a DG

Consultar los permisos de los discos a nivel del SO:

df -k o df -h para listar 
cd /dev/rdsk


for i in `ls -ld emcpower286g emcpower15a emcpower16a |awk {'print$11'}`; do ls -ltr $i* ; done


sqlplus / as sysasm
	
discos_candidatos o former:
	
set lines 400
COLUMN header_status FORMAT a25
COLUMN path FORMAT a35
COLUMN name FORMAT a20
SELECT inst_id, header_status, path, state, OS_MB, create_date 
FROM gv$asm_disk
WHERE header_status = 'CANDIDATE'
ORDER BY path;


