Consultamos tamaño total de DG DATA: (antes y despues de lanzar el script para verificar)

set lines 300
COLUMN name FORMAT a20
SELECT inst_id, name, total_mb, cold_used_mb "USED_MB", free_mb, usable_file_mb "USABLE_MB", state, round((cold_used_mb*100)/total_mb, 2) "%USED", round((free_mb*100)/total_mb, 2) "%FREE"
FROM gv$asm_diskgroup
--WHERE name like '%'
--OR name like '%'
WHERE name = 'DG_DATA_PVIEW'
ORDER BY 1;




